cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with person re-identification using convolutional neural networks and image processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a learning-based spatial polar transformation layer, which involves machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with a dataset, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper involves feature extraction and classification, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also deals with security and privacy, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
